1 - INSTALLATION

before you load the script, make sure you run ~/osiris/default first.
this will copy the osiris default settings to your home directory (~/)
you only need to do this if it's your first time running the script or if
you want to restore the default settings of the script. u *DONT* have to 
run 'default' or './default' everytime you want to use the script. just the 
one time is fine =P

that's more or less it for the installation.

*** NOTE *** not necessary in osiris-1c and later versions *** NOTE ***

