3 - HISTORY

osiris was originally a script for CtoolZ by me and cha0s. we then were in
the process of porting it to an EPIC script, but it sucked and we stopped.
cha0s went on to do incarnate and i went on to do osiris for BitchX. it
didn't exactly work out as planned, so then me and void went on to do
rage/bx. after about a month of working on it, void decided to stick with
his current script embryonic. i kept working on rage, and then i found out
some lameass made or was making a script called rage too... so i decided to
redo osiris, using our shit from rage. that way there's no confusion between
the lameass rage script that someone made and this leet muthafuckin script.
i will be adding in a dated history saying whats added as new versions are
released.

